prompt: Create a timeline infographic showing the progression of intestinal ischemic injury from 0 to 6+ hours. Use a horizontal timeline flowing LEFT to RIGHT with four distinct phases marked by color bands: Phase 1 (0-30 min) in YELLOW (reversible), Phase 2 (30 min-2 hr) in ORANGE (early injury), Phase 3 (2-6 hr) in RED (established injury), Phase 4 (>6 hr) in DARK RED/BLACK (necrosis). Include icons or simplified illustrations showing cellular changes at each phase. Professional medical infographic style., well-composed
